text: Khanyisa Chawane (born 14 January 1996) is a South African netball player. She was selected to represent the South African netball team at the 2019 Netball World Cup. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tzaneen Category:South African netball players Category:2019 Netball World Cup players Category:TeamBath netball players Category:Netball Superleague players Category:South African expatriate sportspeople in England Category:Sportspeople from Limpopo
